      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "description": "Persistent-drift errors by whether the affected user is the room host or a member. Host-heavy = the broadcaster's network is the bottleneck; member-heavy = a follower has chronic latency. Persistent drift suspends the member from further corrections until reconnect.",
